{"tid":806363,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救) 有無巴絲養貓個陣生過癣?","createTime":"2018-09-04T15:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T12:29:25.000Z","uid":132004,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"659680efac16079c50e39a3636331e9cb8eaacc0","tid":806363,"uid":132004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T15:02:30.000Z","msg":"事源我今年6月係朋友到拎養左兩隻美短貓仔<br />\n貓媽媽本身好似有癣，生左之後啲貓仔都有埋癣<br />\n開頭都有帶佢地睇醫生，之後過左一個月左右<br />\n我個身到開始生癬 一開頭唔知係咩以為濕疹定唔知咩<br />\n其實睇過起碼2,3次醫生都只係比藥膏我查<br />\n之後我又上網搵緊好多，買過藥膏都無用<br />\n而家9月份我都係仲生緊，查完隔一排又生返 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我屋企人都中哂，但我係最嚴重個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲打之前都中過? 買藥房買藥膏定去睇醫生 有既可唔可以留個名比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好痕啊真係好崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebdd087a0259573071a7928bc8a145f70ee70385","tid":806363,"uid":132004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T15:24:20.000Z","msg":"up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25b3c5fddb69722d647817e9292b6fa0c39add4","tid":806363,"uid":28351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T15:25:56.000Z","msg":"d癬咩樣架？"},{"pid":"6cba486c3fb36feed7d42f87c618ba492daec2f5","tid":806363,"uid":132004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T15:40:32.000Z","msg":"不要見怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9787f000ae1b30b4c8e3e061e268dde7b56db3d","tid":806363,"uid":201270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T15:52:37.000Z","msg":"之前養貓生過牛皮癬，如果 抵抗力好就唔會生，睇醫生有藥膏擦。好快好番，唔洗擔心"},{"pid":"58f5b291d8694077d928932277d27485dc8f5ad1","tid":806363,"uid":132004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9787f000ae1b30b4c8e3e061e268dde7b56db3d","tid":806363,"uid":201270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T15:52:37.000Z","msg":"之前養貓生過牛皮癬，如果 抵抗力好就唔會生，睇醫生有藥膏擦。好快好番，唔洗擔心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:01:14.000Z","msg":"個陣有冇做啲咩去提高抵抗力? 藥膏有類固醇查左一排  想停左去 真係好痕 前上半身5,6達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4524b2d8acbddc0ccc15594d85a9305e547aa0b4","tid":806363,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:01:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d7b6eb93f9cd578a8ea87ed79fe664188f033aa","tid":806363,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:01:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dde3d78b3cd82026a913bc0c896ee14f34205616","tid":806363,"uid":132004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d7b6eb93f9cd578a8ea87ed79fe664188f033aa","tid":806363,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4524b2d8acbddc0ccc15594d85a9305e547aa0b4","tid":806363,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:01:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:01:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:11:44.000Z","msg":"你點解決? 唔R佢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79813861a16e2721db49e368fa81a37779575846","tid":806363,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:14:30.000Z","msg":"金錢癬係可以傳俾人<br />\n所以咪叫啲人去機構領養<br />\n檢查晒先俾你<br />\n人地有醫生檢查"},{"pid":"15b5ac7a7c8c0e28a8106b584f57ede0014e783a","tid":806363,"uid":201270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T21:49:44.000Z","msg":"我寫錯咗，我都係金錢癬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84c5fde202a9b32c7d73a1f63f6de2f0728d91a","tid":806363,"uid":45684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T01:46:19.000Z","msg":"搽藥膏之餘, 仲要消毒家居環境<br />\n尤其係貓成日磨同訓嘅地方<br />\n注意要用對寵物無害嘅消毒劑"},{"pid":"dce0a2165372b64f3782aac437ab781f57ecfc84","tid":806363,"uid":47433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:26:31.000Z","msg":"我試過，剛剛開始養我隻囡時就惹咗俾我，係金錢癬，幾個月都唔好，睇過醫生搽過幾種藥膏都冇用。而且我本身有哮喘，d類固醇令我喘發得好勁，好無助。<br />\n<br />\n後來享連登有巴打教我用蘋果醋敷，早晚一次，用化妝綿浸濕d蘋果醋敷d癬個位，敷15mins到啦，敷幾日後會紅同更痕，但再敷多排就會慢慢好番斷尾。當然前提係你d貓都要無哂癬先，貓有癬都可以用蘋果醋幫佢地搽下。呢個方法又唔係藥又唔係貴，試下冇壞。"},{"pid":"c4e3f5cf70a939fd18ee23fda743e93f55aad5c2","tid":806363,"uid":106783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:24:15.000Z","msg":"買三條毛shampoo 沖幾次涼好快好<br />\n記得開抽濕，乾爽d 會少d 菌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加油"},{"pid":"36768e64d64c6c48d87784335a780b4441fe4b0c","tid":806363,"uid":92245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:26:26.000Z","msg":"我拎貓貓果d 藥膏人貓2份搽<br />\n一齊搽左個零2個月就好番"},{"pid":"dcf0b84443ae1c0ac7c0cbd718fb0dd4fbb1dfc8","tid":806363,"uid":61554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T12:29:25.000Z","msg":"果時接隻英短返黎果時又係有癬 <br />\n<br />\n好似有聽講過寵物店有隻叫神仙水可以醫癬 但我冇試過唔知係咪有用 去左睇醫生開左藥比佢噴生癬甩毛果d位 <br />\n<br />\n果時耳仔 頸 手腳尾都有 生得好勁 甩毛甩到一岩一忽 用左藥兩個幾三星期就好得7788 依家靚仔返晒"}]}